CSS Vertical Rythm

Version 0.1
By Ricardo Magalhães

/////////////////
// DESCRIPTION //
/////////////////

Helps you set up your CSS typography settings in order to maintain a good looking vertical rythm with body copy and headings.

///////////
// USAGE //
///////////

Simply run the html file and input your desired font sizes, then copy the CSS output.

